---
title: Lamb and Fig Burgers with Feta Aioli and Potato Wedges
description: Honey-sweet fig spread makes a perfect glaze for rich, savoury lamb patties. Creamy feta aioli is a super burger spread, as well as a delicious dipper for the potato wedges!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-a-lagneau-et-aux-figues-f81a608e.jpg
